# Sparkamp macOS Port Plan

## Overview

Port Sparkamp to macOS using SwiftUI while keeping the Rust core. The TUI already works on macOS (cross-platform via ratatui + crossterm). Only the GTK4 GUI needs replacement.

---

## Constraints

- **Audio**: GStreamer via Homebrew (`brew install gstreamer`) — no AVFoundation rewrite
- **Target**: macOS 13.0+
- **Windows**: Native floating windows (separate windows, not tabbed/sidebar)
- **Plugins**: Skipped for v1 (can add later)

---

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  UI Layer                                               │
│  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────────┐  │
│  │  GTK4 (Linux)      │  │  SwiftUI (macOS)       │  │
│  │  ~5500 lines       │  │  ~3700 lines           │  │
│  └─────────────────────┘  └─────────────────────────┘  │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │  TUI (cross-platform — already works on macOS)   │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Core / FFI Layer                                      │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │  core/ (new Rust library — extracts from src/)    │   │
│  │  Builds as .dylib, linked by SwiftUI app         │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Audio Engine                                          │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │  GStreamer (no changes — works on macOS via      │   │
│  │  Homebrew)                                       │   │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## What Already Works on macOS

| Component | Status | Notes |
|-----------|--------|-------|
| TUI | Ready | ratatui + crossterm are cross-platform |
| Core logic | Ready | model, controller, config, media_library, shuffle, skin |
| Plugin system | Ready | libloading works; skip for now |
| SQLite media library | Ready | rusqlite is cross-platform |
| Config/playlist persistence | Ready | dirs crate works |
| ID3/metadata reading | Ready | id3 + symphonia are cross-platform |

