## GStreamer on macOS

### Installation

```bash
brew install gstreamer gst-plugins-base gst-plugins-good
```

### Bundle vs Homebrew

| Option | Pros | Cons |
|--------|-------|------|
| **Homebrew** (chosen) | Simpler bundle (~2MB), updates with system | Extra setup step |
| **Bundle .dylibs** | One-click install, offline | Larger bundle (~50MB) |

For v1: require Homebrew installation. Can bundle later.

### GStreamer Components Needed

- `gstreamer` — core
- `gst-plugins-base` — playbin, audioconvert, volume
- `gst-plugins-good` — equalizer-10bands, MP3 (libmad)
- `gst-plugins-bad` — additional formats

